title: MacBook Air 820 00165 PPBUS_G3H 1V
message:

It has orange light on magsafe.

Is there anything else I can check?

title: MacBook Air 820 00165 PPBUS_G3H 1V
message:
First of all, welcome to the forum!

"27- 1"
Be sure no short between R7120 and L7130.
Then change Q7180.
